{"tid":1333924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遮唔係用嚟擋而係用嚟趕狗","createTime":"2019-07-20T02:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T03:00:23.000Z","uid":267263,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac567bd0295792c0d73d03b1a5d13c1df67dd96","tid":1333924,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"行山見到野狗,有人開遮擋,結果對隻狗<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毫無作用</span></span></strong>,仲比癫狗咬爛把遮再咬傷個人<br />\n之後行山客將把遮當成<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打狗棍</span></span></strong>,發現原來啲狗一直係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">欺善怕惡</span></span></strong>,<br />\n如果只係擋啲狗根本唔會驚,仲愈咬愈<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">興奮</span></span></strong>。<br />\n有咗打狗棍終於可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗衡</span></span></strong>到野狗,保護到自己又保護到其他人。<br />\n有時會有人4-5隻<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">特別癲</span></span></strong>嘅野狗突然衝出嚟,<br />\n以前啲人只會一邊後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">退</span></span></strong>一邊比狗咬到傷晒。<br />\n但有咗打狗棍,衝出嚟嘅野狗只係嚟<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">送頭</span></span></strong>,啲人緊係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">教訓</span></span></strong>下隻冇人性嘅野狗。<br />\n但係有人係e個時候又會大叫話啲野狗只係揾食姐叫人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">停手</span></span></strong>。<br />\n可惜啲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇人性</span></span></strong>嘅野狗唔會因為你嘅同情而放過行山客。<br />\n反而,令到行山客唔趕狗,令到更多人比癫狗<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咬傷</span></span></strong>。<br />\n所以見到有人叫人冷靜,請帶佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">離開</span></span></strong>,<br />\n因為佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對狗嘅同情,係對手足最大嘅傷害</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遮唔係用嚟擋而係用嚟趕狗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5fb0a2cfbde1ed9444b16ebd6ad87274c63f27a4","tid":1333924,"uid":267263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"02468874e6e761ba8fb6a70e1e6676609e47800c","tid":1333924,"uid":267263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:29:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f29ccc2ba423a88fe0118904b42c6b8226461b5e","tid":1333924,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"對敵人善良即對自己殘忍<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n<br />\n大叫便衣警殺人"},{"pid":"c0c3fdaf7bb8fb5557005bc3b17c29582ea38d07","tid":1333924,"uid":267263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f33f83f83efaadfa558d98db04f9582a614ecbd","tid":1333924,"uid":13490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"有人冒警<br />\n你扮警察<br />\n冇委任證<br />\n涉嫌傷人<br />\n藏有攻擊性武器<br />\n我地行使公民逮捕權"},{"pid":"152d67bc67cde652948de80beae2f17f93542e33","tid":1333924,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf6dd70c42201788640aa05e0c56c0c06a45f84d","tid":1333924,"uid":267263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:32:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ebce48eca09c930ad269b54cc25c7561d3c8c4c","tid":1333924,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［戰略］見好多手足獨自野餐 建議組隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8fd4530d73e9082104e901d52961749dd029538","tid":1333924,"uid":